'''Henry Alan Gilroy''' developed the [[Star Wars: The Clone Wars (film)|''Star Wars: The Clone Wars'' movie]] and [[Star Wars: The Clone Wars|animated series]], working at the [[Skywalker Ranch|Skywalker]] and [[Big Rock Ranch]] facilities with [[George Lucas]]. He served as head writer for [[The Clone Wars: Season One|Season One]], penning several episodes. He is also the author of several ''Star Wars'' comic books. He was a co-Executive Producer of ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]'' starting with [[Star Wars Rebels Season Two|Season Two]].

